[[File:Lufthansa_Boeing_737-300;_D-ABED@ZRH;04.03.2013_694bc_(8531080414).jpg|thumb]] [[窄體飛機|窄體飛機]]<br>後：[[波音777-300ER|波音777-300ER]] 廣體飛機]]

'''廣體飛機'''（Wide-body aircraft），指的是機身直徑有5至6公尺以上的飛機。對於客機而言，代表至少會有兩條走道，在[[經濟艙|經濟艙]]的座位一排會有7至10個。廣體客機通常可搭載200至800人<ref name="travelPro">{{cite book| title = A Guide to Becoming a Travel Professional| author1 = Ginger Gorham| author2 = Ginger Todd| author3 = Susan Rice| publisher = Cengage Learning| year = 2003| ISBN = 9781401851774| page = [https://archive.org/details/guidetobecomingt0000gorh/page/40 40]| url = https://archive.org/details/guidetobecomingt0000gorh/page/40}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url = http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F20E15F93C59107A93CBA81788D85F468785F9&scp=133&sq=wide-body&st=p| title = the traveler's world; Test of a New Wide-Bodied Airbus| author = Paul J. C. Friedlander| newspaper = New York Times| date = 1972-03-19| accessdate = 2020-11-01| archive-date = 2013-12-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131221133513/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F20E15F93C59107A93CBA81788D85F468785F9&scp=133&sq=wide-body&st=p}}</ref><ref>{{cite book| page = [https://archive.org/details/flyingoffcoursee00doga/page/n186 170]| title = Flying Off Course: The Economics of International Airlines| url = https://archive.org/details/flyingoffcoursee00doga| url-access = limited| author = Doganis, Rigas| publisher = Routledge| year = 2002| ISBN = 9780415213240}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.airbus.com/aircraftfamilies/passengeraircraft/a380family/a380-800/specifications/ |title=Dimensions & key data | Airbus, a leading aircraft manufacturer |publisher=Airbus.com |date=2012-09-27 |accessdate=2012-10-01 |archive-date=2012-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120708071501/http://www.airbus.com/aircraftfamilies/passengeraircraft/a380family/a380-800/specifications/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，相对於[[窄體客機|窄體客機]]，窄體客機直徑為3至4 m（10至13英尺），只有一個走道，座位一排會有2至6人<ref name="travelPro" /><ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.businessdictionary.com/definition/narrowbody-aircraft.html|title = narrowbody aircraft|accessdate = 2009-03-18|archive-date = 2017-06-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170618035008/http://www.businessdictionary.com/definition/narrowbody-aircraft.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book| page = 552| title = Flight International| author = [[Royal_Aero_Club|Royal Aero Club]] (Great Britain), Royal Aero Club of the United Kingdom| year = 1967| publisher = IPC Transport Press Ltd.| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=U3s7AAAAMAAJ&pgis=1}}</ref>。

第一型廣體客機為[[波音747|波音747]]，發布於1969年。之後三發動機的廣體客機如[[DC-10|DC-10]]及[[L-1011|L-1011]]陸續問世。[[波音公司|波音公司]]的主要競爭對手之一[[空中巴士|空中巴士]]於1974年發布了第一架雙發動機的廣體客機[[A300|A300]]。

由於[[引擎|引擎]]的可靠度不高，[[雙發噴射機|雙發噴射機]]以往只可執行備降機場之間不超過60分鐘航程的航線。隨着引擎技術的進步，雙引擎飛機最終獲監管機構同意，可執行[[双发延程飞行|長程飛行]]。航空公司為求營運成本降低，除了大型的[[波音747|波音747]]及[[空中巴士|空中巴士]][[A380|A380]]以外，已逐漸改為操作雙發動機的廣體客機為主。

